headline: What to Expect From Weyerhaeuser’s Next Quarterly Earnings Report
summary: Weyerhaeuser is set to report its fourth-quarter earnings next month, and expectations are grim, with analysts projecting a triple-digit plunge in funds from operations that could push FFO into negative territory.
